info.description:
REST API specification for the Chapaa Moyo fundraising platform.

Base URL: {{base_url}}

All protected endpoints require: Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

All amounts are in TZS (Tanzanian Shilling) as integers. No decimals.

Timestamps are ISO 8601: 2026-05-07T10:42:00Z

Consistent response envelope:
  Success: { success: true, data: {...}, meta: {...} }
  Error:   { success: false, error: { code: "...", message: "..." } }

